cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.CR 

The paper deals with citation data and statistical analysis of citation impact, which are relevant to several sub-categories in computer science. cs.DL (Digital Libraries) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely categories as they deal with bibliometrics and citation analysis. cs.CY (Computational Geometry) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) are also possible categories as they involve statistical analysis. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as it deals with statistical analysis and modeling.
